contents:
[package]
name = "fischl"
description = "Helper library to manage compatibility and downloads for KeqingLauncher"
authors = [ "TukanDev",]
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"

[build-dependencies]
prost-build = "0.14"
protoc-bin-vendored = "3"

[dependencies]
reqwest-middleware = "0.4"
reqwest-retry = "0.7"
sysinfo = "0.37"
serde_json = "1.0"
thiserror = "1.0"
futures-util = "0.3"
futures = "0.3"

[features]
compat = [ "dep:wincompatlib",]
download = [ "dep:zip", "dep:tar", "dep:flate2", "dep:liblzma", "dep:zstd", "dep:chksum-md5", "dep:prost", "dep:crossbeam-deque",]
default = [ "download",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12"
features = [ "blocking", "json", "stream", "native-tls-vendored",]

[dependencies.chksum-md5]
version = "0.1.0"
features = [ "async-runtime-tokio",]
optional = true

[dependencies.prost]
version = "0.14"
features = []
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.45"
features = [ "macros",]

[dependencies.zip]
version = "4.6"
default-features = false
features = [ "deflate",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tar]
version = "0.4.44"
optional = true

[dependencies.flate2]
version = "1.1.2"
default-features = false
features = [ "zlib-rs",]
optional = true

[dependencies.liblzma]
version = "0.4"
features = [ "static",]
optional = true

[dependencies.zstd]
version = "0.13.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.crossbeam-deque]
version = "0.8.6"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.wincompatlib]
version = "0.7.7"
features = [ "all",]
optional = true
